    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. The exterior has a clean finish with minor surface scratches consistent with normal use. The interior shows light wear on the upholstery and trim but is generally well-maintained. Mechanically, the car runs reliably with no major issues noted.",
